rl_meta":{"origin":41191,"position":0},"title":"Ahmad on Love: True love for Allah seeks no worldly benefits","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Maruwidhi reported: Imam Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah have mercy on him, was asked about love for the sake of Allah and he said, \u201cIt is that you not love him for the sake of some worldly benefit.\u201d Source: T\u0323abaqa\u0304t al-H\u0323ana\u0304bilah 1\/60 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0631\u0648\u0630\u064a \u0642\u062f \u0633\u0626\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0645\u0627\u0645 \u0623\u062d\u0645\u062f \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u062d\u0646\u0628\u0644\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27832,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/18\/khawlani-zuhd-trust-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":41191,"position":1},"title":"Khawlani on Zuhd: Asceticism is to trust Allah over yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ahmad ibn Hanbal reported: Abu Muslim al-Khawlani, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cTo renounce the world does not mean to forbid what is allowed, nor to squander wealth. Verily, to renounce the world means to be more reliant on what is in the hand of Allah than your\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38862,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/21\/imam-ahmad-dua-r